%% KubeRay Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant HTTPRoute as HTTPRoute<br/>/ray/{ns}/{cluster}
    participant KubeRBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pod
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant CertMgr as cert-manager<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Submitter as Submitter Job Pod

    Note over User, RayHead: Flow 1: Ray Dashboard Access via Gateway API

    User->>Gateway: GET /ray/{ns}/{cluster}<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS
    Gateway->>HTTPRoute: Route matching
    HTTPRoute->>KubeRBACProxy: Forward to sidecar<br/>8443/TCP
    KubeRBACProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>get services/{cluster}-head-svc
    K8sAPI-->>KubeRBACProxy: Allowed
    KubeRBACProxy->>RayHead: Forward to dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    RayHead-->>KubeRBACProxy: Dashboard response
    KubeRBACProxy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: HTML/JSON response

    Note over Operator, Submitter: Flow 2: RayJob Submission (K8sJobMode)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob CR<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: RayJob created
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>HTTPS/443
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Submitter Job<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Submitter: Pod scheduled
    Submitter->>RayHead: Submit job via dashboard<br/>HTTP/8265

    Note over Operator, CertMgr: Flow 3: mTLS Certificate Provisioning

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Detect RayCluster with mTLS
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create SelfSigned Issuer
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create CA Certificate
    CertMgr-->>Operator: CA Secret created
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create Head Certificate<br/>(90d duration, 15d renewal)
    Operator->>CertMgr: Create Worker Certificate<br/>(90d duration, 15d renewal)

    Note over RayHead, RayWorker: Flow 4: Ray Cluster Internal Communication

    RayWorker->>RayHead: GCS connection<br/>6379/TCP (plaintext or mTLS)
    RayWorker->>RayHead: Object Store<br/>8076/TCP (plaintext or mTLS)
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Task dispatch<br/>10002/TCP (plaintext or mTLS)
